sentence: Three  Palestinians  have  been  killed  in  an  Israeli  drone  attack  on  the  Jenin  refugee  camp  in  the  West  Bank,  according  to  Palestinian  medical  sources.
Meanwhile  Israel  says  its  security  forces  have  killed  three  gunmen  who  opened  fire  at  a  checkpoint  on  a  road  leading  into  Jerusalem  from  the  West  Bank.
